name: Valkyrian Archon Blueprint Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct secondary and elite hulls, weapons, and fighter LPCs form the Valkyrian Archon Industries.

name: Valkyrian Horizon Blueprint Package

name: Valkyrian Enigma Blueprint Package
